# StyleGuru — AI Powered Outfit Recommender
# CLAUDE.md — Read this before writing any code

## What this app does
StyleGuru helps Sri Lankan men build a digital wardrobe from photos of their
own clothes. The AI (Claude API) then suggests complete outfit combinations
from their actual wardrobe based on occasion and weather.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React Native + Expo (TypeScript)
- Backend: Python + FastAPI (separate project: StyleGuru-Backend/)
- Database: Supabase (PostgreSQL)
- Photo storage: Cloudinary
- Clothing recognition: Google Vision API (called from backend)
- Outfit suggestions: Claude API / claude-sonnet-4-20250514 (called from backend)
- Weather: OpenWeatherMap (called from frontend)
- Navigation: expo-router (file-based routing)
- State: Zustand (global) + useState (local)
- HTTP: axios

